00:31:21.500 --> 00:31:25.910 align:middle line:84%
And it was about modern
science and Eastern mysticism.

00:31:25.910 --> 00:31:28.430 align:middle line:84%
And there were lots and
lots of speakers there.

00:31:28.430 --> 00:31:30.290 align:middle line:84%
And it was my
first trip to India

00:31:30.290 --> 00:31:32.240 align:middle line:90%
and a big experience for me.

00:31:32.240 --> 00:31:35.200 align:middle line:84%
And that's another
thing I owe to Stan.

